name: 23S rRNA (pseudouridine1915-N3)-methyltransferase
reaction: S-adenosyl-L-methionine + pseudouridine1915 in 23S rRNA = S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + N3-methylpseudouridine1915 in 23S rRNA
comment: YbeA does not methylate uridine at position 1915 [1].

references.title: Identification of pseudouridine methyltransferase in Escherichia coli.
YbeA is the m3Psi methyltransferase RlmH that targets nucleotide 1915 in 23S rRNA.
